              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 9Be targets of 0.171+-0.035 mg/cm2 thicknesses",
                "were made by evaporating high-purity",
                "beryllium onto a five-mil copper backing"
              ]
            }
          ],
